Lo estaba guardando.

301
00:24:29,084 --> 00:24:30,381
¿Por dos años?

302
00:24:31,319 --> 00:24:32,718
Brian...

303
00:24:34,489 --> 00:24:35,888
Dios.

304
00:24:36,458 --> 00:24:38,824
